My son LOVED it. 
Everything was included perfectly. Shipping was quick. The blanket it comes with is way bigger than I expected. Beanie is great quality. The plushy is adorable, just had a minor defect on the crown. But it didnt change how much my son loved it. Stickers the hologram card are included in the game case. The pin is cool, it spins. We pinned it to the lanyard. Overall my son said it's incredible.
